title: Hannah Davis and Derek Jeter Are Expecting Their First Child
text: Hannah Davis and Derek Jeter Are Expecting Their First Child Getty By Alyssa Bailey Feb 13, 2017 Hannah Davis and Derek Jeter are expecting a daughter, the model announced today in a post on The Player Tribune . "Now, pregnant with our first child, Derek and I are looking to the future," she wrote. And the former Yankee is so excited he's already picked out a name, Davis says: "He already has a name in mindâ€”he's set on it. (We'll see.) He'll say when he calls me during the day: 'So, how are you and so-and-so doing?' 'That's not the name yet, sweetie.' Whatever her name is, I know she'll run circles around him."
